Dependencies:
- Python 2.6+
- Tornado Web http://www.tornadoweb.org
- TornadIO https://github.com/MrJoes/tornadio

Known issues:
- When text goes oveflows the chat box, other clients will not see it anymore
- User names are not displayed

How to run on CentOS with python2.7:
sudo /opt/python27/bin/python2.7 server.py